# Hermes Meta Ads Kit — Environment Variables
#
# Most read-only authentication is handled by social-cli (no API keys needed here).
# Run: social auth login

# Default ad account (optional — can also set via social-cli)
# META_AD_ACCOUNT=act_123456789

# Required for direct Graph API workflows such as ad-upload/ad-copy-generator
# when they bypass social-cli token lookup.
# FACEBOOK_ACCESS_TOKEN=EAAB...

# Optional: where scripts/install-hermes-skills.sh installs skills.
# HERMES_HOME=/home/you/.hermes
# HERMES_SKILL_CATEGORY=marketing
